Ali Maffucci dropped from a size 14/16 to a size 8/10 in just three months . 
  She lost 11 kg (24 lbs) in three months by replacing pasta, bread and rice with spiralized vegetables for every meal . 
  The 28-year-old lost weight after quitting her corporate job and writing a healthy lifestyle book . 
  She went from a weight of 12 stone to 10 stone (almost two stone) and is now a size 10 . 
 